<br>
The shield skill gives you some really cool combat moves that you couldn't use otherwise.  I don't know if it helps you block.  Parry is good stuff, it works quite well.  I'm double speccing in parry and celtic spear with my hero, and I'm pretty happy.  I don't know how it compares to shield.<br>
<br>
Intercept lets you take hits that otherwise would have hit another player.  Target that player, hit the intercept button, and make sure you're close to him/her.  This skill is a little tricky to master, I still haven't got it down.<br>
<br>
No idea what guard does. <p>Ahry - hero of Gaoth an Iar, Percival server <BR>
